Class ImmutableTypedProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Dictionary<K,V>

          • nl.esciencecenter.octopus.ImmutableTypedProperties
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Map<Object,Object>

    public class ImmutableTypedProperties
extends Properties
    Read-only properties implementation. Also contains some utility functions for getting typed properties.
